<!--<h4>Panel-I.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīmat<unclear>taila</unclear>padēva pṛtuvīrājyaṁge
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yye Eṟegāri naḻgavuṇḍugeyye Eṟecaṭṭa
<lb n="3"/>Ūrggāvuṇḍugeye svasti sakanripakālātītasaṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>vatsara sataṅgaEṇṭanūrō 903 mūṟane viṣuva
<lb n="5" break="no"/>saṁvatsaraṁ pravarttise <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<!--<h4>Panel-II.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="6"/>vaisākamāsada sudha dasamiyuṁ bṛhaspativāramaṁ
<lb n="7"/>Uttaranakṣatramu Illiyya tuṟugoḷ
<lb n="8"/>gōsāsi dugaṇa sattu svarggamaṁ paḍedaṁ
<lb n="9"/>Aṇnayya bareda sivabhṛpta
<lb n="10"/>ni <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> kalla ja <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ti <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> badagoṁdu gavaṁ <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> 
</p>

